# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:23
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Rješavanje problema"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:25
msgid ""
"If you are experiencing an issue with OpenShot, such as a freeze, crash, or "
"error message, there are many different techniques which can be useful for "
"troubleshooting the issue."
msgstr ""
"Ako imate problema s OpenShotom, poput zamrzavanja, pada ili poruke o "
"pogrešci, postoji mnogo različitih tehnika koje mogu biti korisne za "
"rješavanje problema."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:29
msgid "Windows 11 Unresponsive"
msgstr "Windows 11 ne reagira"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you experience a freeze on Windows 11, this is a known issue with PyQt5 "
"and Windows 11, related to the accessibility features in Qt. This is "
"triggered by pressing :kbd:`Ctrl+C` in OpenShot (*only on Windows 11*). "
"OpenShot will become unresponsive and a memory leak is also present (i.e. "
"the longer OpenShot is unresponsive, the larger your memory leak will become "
"until OpenShot finally crashes or the user kills the process)."
msgstr ""
"Ako dođe do zamrzavanja na Windows 11, to je poznati problem s PyQt5 i "
"Windows 11, vezan uz pristupačne značajke u Qt-u. To se pokreće pritiskom "
"na :kbd:`Ctrl+C` u OpenShotu (*samo na Windows 11*). OpenShot će prestati "
"reagirati, a prisutan je i curenje memorije (što duže OpenShot ne reagira, "
"to će curenje memorije biti veće dok OpenShot na kraju ne padne ili korisnik "
"ne prekine proces)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:36
msgid ""
"A simple work-around is to avoid :kbd:`Ctrl+C` on Windows 11, and instead "
"use the right-click Copy/Paste menus. Another work-around is to remap your "
"\"Copy\" from :kbd:`Ctrl+C` to something else, for example :kbd:`Alt+C`. You "
"can change your keyboard mappings in the OpenShot Preferences. See :ref:"
"`preferences_keyboard_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Jednostavno rješenje je izbjegavati :kbd:`Ctrl+C` na Windows 11 i umjesto "
"toga koristiti izbornike Kopiraj/Zalijepi desnim klikom. Drugo rješenje je "
"premapirati \"Kopiraj\" s :kbd:`Ctrl+C` na nešto drugo, na primjer :kbd:"
"`Alt+C`. Mape tipkovnice možete promijeniti u postavkama OpenShota. "
"Pogledajte :ref:`preferences_keyboard_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:41
msgid "Windows Debugging with GDB"
msgstr "Otklanjanje pogrešaka na Windowsu s GDB-om"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:43
msgid ""
"If you are experiencing a crash or freeze with OpenShot in Windows 10/11, "
"the following step by step instructions will help you determine the cause of "
"the crash. These instructions will display a stack trace of OpenShot's "
"source code, at the location of the crash. This information can be extremely "
"useful for our development team, and very useful to attach to bug reports "
"(for a quicker resolution)."
msgstr ""
"Ako doživljavate pad ili zamrzavanje OpenShota na Windows 10/11, sljedeće "
"upute korak po korak pomoći će vam odrediti uzrok pada. Ove upute prikazat "
"će stog poziva izvornog koda OpenShota na mjestu pada. Ove informacije mogu "
"biti izuzetno korisne našem razvojnom timu i vrlo korisne za priložiti uz "
"izvještaje o pogreškama (za brže rješavanje)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:49
msgid "Install the Latest Daily Build"
msgstr "Instalirajte najnoviju dnevnu verziju"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:51
msgid ""
"Before attaching a debugger, please download the **latest version** of "
"OpenShot: https://www.openshot.org/download#daily. Install this version of "
"OpenShot to the default location: ``C:\\Program Files\\OpenShot Video "
"Editor\\``. For details instructions on debugging OpenShot on Windows, "
"please see `this wiki <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Windows-"
"Debugging-with-GDB>`_."
msgstr ""
"Prije pridruživanja otklanjanju pogrešaka, preuzmite **najnoviju verziju** "
"OpenShota: https://www.openshot.org/download#daily. Instalirajte ovu verziju "
"OpenShota na zadanu lokaciju: ``C:\\Program Files\\OpenShot Video "
"Editor\\``. Za detaljne upute o otklanjanju pogrešaka OpenShota na Windowsu, "
"pogledajte `ovu wiki stranicu <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/"
"Windows-Debugging-with-GDB>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
